PATCHNUM=1346
LSPINFO=include/linux/lsppatchlevel.h
TMPFILE=/tmp/mvl_patch_$$

function dopatch() {
    patch $* >${TMPFILE} 2>&1 <<"EOF"
MR: 26835
Disposition: Backport from 2.6.22-rc1
Adjustments:

From 86e1f0df2f88fd86657ddb993bba468a75128e02 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
